# graphify ignore — keep vendored / generated noise out of the knowledge graph.
# Precedence: .graphifyignore wins over .gitignore. node_modules/, dist/, build/,
# __pycache__/, .pytest_cache/, graphify-out/ are already auto-skipped by graphify.

# Vendored frontend bundles — minified, zero architectural signal.
# These 3 files alone added ~1,421 nodes (9% of the graph, 14.8% of code nodes)
# and corrupted the god-node ranking with single-letter minified functions.
app/web_ui/vendor/
**/*.min.js
**/*.min.css

# Astro build cache + output (web/dist is auto-skipped by dirname; .astro is not).
web/.astro/
web/dist/

# Graph scratch / sidecars that are not source.
graphify-out/
